Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:03.11,0:00:05.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎來到羅德斯島
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:05.71,0:00:08.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼緊接著\N就請觀賞第二部份吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:08.92,0:00:11.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,~歡迎來到羅德斯島~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.86,0:00:12.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噗噗噗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:16.11,0:00:17.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自由騎士潘恩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:17.56,0:00:20.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,史派克\N一段時間不見你變強壯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:21.13,0:00:22.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,見習騎士的史派克
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:23.24,0:00:27.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年若還是不行的話\N明年還得多加油喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:27.93,0:00:30.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉，別這麼失落打起精神嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.90,0:00:32.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊，明年一定沒問題的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.51,0:00:37.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在怎麼說只有\N潘恩才能成為騎士嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:38.38,0:00:41.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭討厭我才不要等到明年呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:41.85,0:00:44.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想當騎士，現在就想要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:45.95,0:00:47.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,買啦買啦，買騎士給我啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:47.61,0:00:49.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能用買的嗎?真是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:49.17,0:00:50.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:51.59,0:00:53.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別灰心啊，史派克
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:53.43,0:00:54.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陛下，有事相求
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:54.61,0:00:57.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請給我這史派克\N今年再一次機會吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.43,0:01:00.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很可惜今年的考試已經結束\N不能認可特例
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.43,0:01:02.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別這麼說嘛，陛下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:02.42,0:01:06.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請給我個特例認可的鼓勵\N(特例音同鼓勵)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:07.67,0:01:09.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 什麼?\N- 有兩下子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:10.61,0:01:12.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了…都這麼說了\N也沒辦法了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.17,0:01:13.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿，成了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:14.88,0:01:17.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我這卡修給予的補考\N可是沒有中途停止的喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:18.30,0:01:18.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:18.82,0:01:20.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已有不論怎樣的試煉\N都可忍受的覺悟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:20.86,0:01:21.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:21.52,0:01:26.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼，在這裡有我可愛的女兒\N妮絲所烤的餅乾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:26.89,0:01:31.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請和我一起將這個送到大龍山\N的龍媽媽那裡去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:32.23,0:01:32.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:33.50,0:01:34.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來，走吧，史派克
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:34.83,0:01:36.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦?餅乾?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.99,0:01:39.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不得不賜予你如此艱鉅的任務
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.17,0:01:43.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也可是很心疼的，史派克…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.71,0:01:47.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若能通過這試煉\N一定能當過優秀的騎士喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.99,0:01:49.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說笑的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.12,0:01:54.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛頭小子去陪小孩子玩\N真是最適合不過了，哈哈哈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.59,0:01:59.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,記得再看喔
